{"id":13543,"date":"2020-12-02T11:11:45","date_gmt":"2020-12-02T10:11:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/?page_id=13543"},"modified":"2025-02-05T16:30:31","modified_gmt":"2025-02-05T15:30:31","slug":"mannheimer-swartling-in-society","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/en\/sustainability\/mannheimer-swartling-in-society\/","title":{"rendered":"MSA in Society"},"content":{"rendered":"<p class=\"preamble\">As one of the most prominent actors in the legal industry, and a major business operator, we have both a responsibility and an opportunity to influence social change in a positive direction. MSA in Society is the third and final pillar of our sustainability framework.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28077 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/10\/stockholm-hustak-1200x825.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1200\" height=\"825\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/10\/stockholm-hustak-1200x825.jpg 1200w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/10\/stockholm-hustak-2000x1376.jpg 2000w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/10\/stockholm-hustak-800x550.jpg 800w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/10\/stockholm-hustak-768x528.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/10\/stockholm-hustak-1536x1056.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/app\/uploads\/2024\/10\/stockholm-hustak-2048x1409.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Aside from our role as a business law adviser, we actively contribute to a better society through pro bono partnerships with several important organisations. We participate across a number of different areas including climate and the environment, social affairs and human rights. Under the umbrella of MSA Arts, we are also involved in several partnerships to promote a vibrant cultural life and to strengthen the role of culture in the business community and society at large.<\/p>\n<p>The provision of pro bono advice is deeply embedded in our corporate culture and our staff are highly encouraged to get involved. We have supported many organisations since the firm\u2019s foundation in 1990 and several hundred of our employees have contributed.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>As one of the most prominent actors in the legal industry, and a major business operator, we have both a responsibility and an opportunity to\u2026<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":13522,"menu_order":7,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-13543","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"acf":[],"lang":"en","translations":{"en":13543,"sv":8837},"pll_sync_post":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13543"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13543"}],"version-history":[{"count":57,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13543\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":29708,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13543\/revisions\/29708"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/13522"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.mannheimerswartling.se\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13543"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}